// Copy to Signing.xcconfig (gitignored) and fill in your team.
// `make ios-project` seeds Signing.xcconfig from this file automatically.
//
// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM: Xcode ▸ Settings ▸ Accounts ▸ select team ▸ "Team ID"
// (10 characters, e.g. AB12CD34EF). With it set, `make ios-archive` signs
// automatically and Xcode device runs need no manual signing step —
// and it survives `make ios-project` regenerating the .xcodeproj.
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM =
